<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Returns `true` for every status code that has a dedicated named constructor in `Status`.\nUsed to ensure `Status.other` is never constructed with a code that already has a name.\n","docLink":"./Std/Http/Data/Status.html#Std.Http.isKnownStatusCode","kind":"def","line":38,"name":"Std.Http.isKnownStatusCode","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Std/Http/Data/Status.lean#L38-L49"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Std/Http/Data/Status.html#Std.Http.IsValidReasonPhrase\"><span class=\"name\">Std</span>.<span class=\"name\">Http</span>.<span class=\"name\">IsValidReasonPhrase</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">s</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Prop</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"A proposition stating that `s` is a valid HTTP reason phrase: every character passes\n`Char.reasonPhraseChar` per RFC 9110 §15.\n\nReference: https://httpwg.org/specs/rfc9110.html#reason.phrase\n","docLink":"./Std/Http/Data/Status.html#Std.Http.IsValidReasonPhrase","kind":"def","line":29,"name":"Std.Http.IsValidReasonPhrase","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Std/Http/Data/Status.lean#L29-L36"}}],"imports":["Std.Http.Internal"],"instances":[{"className":"Repr","name":"Std.Http.instReprCustomStatus","typeNames":["Std.Http.CustomStatus"]},{"className":"BEq","name":"Std.Http.instBEqCustomStatus","typeNames":["Std.Http.CustomStatus"]},{"className":"Inhabited","name":"Std.Http.instInhabitedCustomStatus","typeNames":["Std.Http.CustomStatus"]},{"className